Appliction Idea¶

The application will be the following:

  • check if a person male or female get its correct daily calories
    • for a man: ~2 700 Kcal
    • for a woman: ~2000 Kcal We base our needs of features on this article:
      • https://healthyeating.sfgate.com/gives-energy-per-gram-fat-protein-carbohydrates-8319.html

To create this app, we need the following features:

  • product_name
  • proteins_100g
  • fat_100g
  • carbohydrates_100g
  • energy_100g
  • image_url

At the end we have to be able to say if the appilcation is possible with such data

taking care of outliers:

In [19]:
from scipy import stats
def find_outliers(data,var):
  iqr=stats.iqr(data[var])
  q1=data[var].quantile(0.25)
  q3=data[var].quantile(0.75)
  lower=q1-iqr*1.5
  upper=q3+iqr*1.5
  dfOutliers=data[(data[var]<lower) | (data[var]>upper)]
  return dfOutliers
